title: ELEMENT 'NYJAH HUSTON' MAKE IT COUNT - 2012 INTERNATIONAL SKATE CONTEST SERIES
description:
Nyjah Huston gives a glimpse into the Element "MAKE IT COUNT" International Contest Series.

Overall contest winner receives an all expenses paid trip to join fellow winners from around the globe at Element YMCA camp for the chance to compete for Element sponsorship, followed by a day at The Berrics with the Element team, August 2012.
